5. Login sayfası: "Kurumsal Hesapla Giriş Yap" → `GET /api/v1/auth/oidc/login` redirect
6. `S-AUTH-CALLBACK` (`Docs/06_SCREEN_CATALOG.md` §S-AUTH-CALLBACK)
7. `InternalLayout` iskeleti + `/app/dashboard` boş placeholder

