- `Docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` §8.3 (frontend contract)

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** PermissionGate/RoleGuard (Faz 2), S-SESSION-EXPIRED modal (Faz 10), case/task ekranları, seed.

**Stop:** [ ] Browser: login → IdP (dev Google) → callback → dashboard; [ ] logout → login; [ ] 401 interceptor redirect çalışır. PR/onay → İterasyon 5.

